    narr:narration """This hub aggregates strategic alignment assessments across artifacts and interactions, consistently anchoring to the thesis of \"narrative as steering vector.\" The [YC application strategy](narr:Assessment_StrategicAlignment_YC) and [founder career-arc](narr:Rubric_StrategicAlignment_ScarletDame) establish the foundational intellectual through-line, while [pilot planning](narr:Rubric_StrategicAlignment_PilotPlan) and [GTM modeling](narr:RubricAssess_Strategy_GTM) translate this into operational pricing and expansion pathways. Tactical validation occurs through [architecture-team beachheads](narr:RubricAssess_StrategicAlignment_WeeklyCall) and [founder-led beta feedback](narr:Rubric_StrategicAlignment_FounderBetaUser), which refine the ICP toward operations personas. Enterprise-grade requirements—specifically on-prem compliance and AI-to-AI provenance—are integrated via [customer architect engagements](narr:Rubric_StrategicAlignment_CustomerArchitect). The [YC demo beats](narr:Rubric_StrategicAlignment_YCDemoBeats) and [YC call transcripts](narr:Rubric_StrategicAlignment_YC_Call) serve as the most recent synthesis of these threads, mapping product vision directly to organizational authority. While all entries reflect high alignment, the focus shifts between the high-level [positioning thesis](narr:RubricAssess_StrategicAlignment) and specific [revenue/TAM modeling](narr:Assess_Strategy_RevenueModelTAM).""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Assess_Strategy_RevenueModelTAM> ;
